spell.description:
$?c1[Soul Shards are generated by your Agony's damage over time.

]?c2[Soul Shards are generated by your Shadow Bolt.

]?c3[Soul Shard Fragments are generated by many of your spells.

][]Soul Shards are consumed to cast your most powerful spells and summon demons to serve you.

While out of combat you regenerate up to 3 Soul Shards.
